file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
- url: 'http://localhost:8000/v2/api'
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
paths:
  /adopt:
    get:
      tags:
      - pet
      summary: Find pet by ID
      description: It gets pets
      operationId: getPetById
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/limit'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful operation
components:
  parameters:
    limit:
      name: playerId
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
